channel.title: KBD...Isn't a KBD model?
channel.description:
Hello, I would like some help regarding a pretty important issue.
My King Black Dragon model isnt the KBD model, it's somekind of 2 headed cat....with a shield around it.
I was wondering if someone could guide me to the way of changing npc models? (I dont mean adding new ones, just changing the identity of an npc)
